//
//  Builds a parabolic plate 
//  according to the formula:
//         y= kx^2
//
//  Where the focal length is 1/(4*k)
//   
//
//  This code is designed for 
//  ease of use, not for computational
//  efficiency. You must be patient 
//  when rendering!
//=============================

